title: Your Expression of Interest is published
title2: Your EoI has been sent to suppliers
title2_line1: Quote this number, along with your project ID (XXXXXXXX) if you need to contact CCS for support.

title3_contents.text: The suppliers you selected can read your RfI and ask questions if they need more information.
When the clarification period ends you will need to answer the supplier questions by the deadline you set.
